reviewText: Kelly's right coolest shoes ever! Fast shipping.

The moves will definitely give you a workout, but I don't feel the instructor caters to beginner level at all. The pace is WAY too fast and the moves are not well explained; she just speeds straight thru and I doubt she understands what it feels like to NOT be limber already.
Great instructional  dvds.  Its like having a personal trainer in your home. Love  these dvds and love cleo.
